# {{wiki_name}} wiki, operating schema

This file is the contract between the user and the agent operating on this wiki. The agent reads it on every session and follows it strictly.

Shared logic (provenance markers, confidence scoring, lifecycle states, source quality buckets, source ID normalization, manifest schema, retrieval cost escalation, structured log format, page templates, cross-linking rules, project lifecycle, modes of operation, image ingestion, monthly archival, hot.md spec) lives in the plugin's `skills/wiki-core/SKILL.md`. This file covers only wiki-specific configuration and must not duplicate SKILL.md content.

## Hard boundary

This folder is the entire scope of the agent's operations. Everything outside this folder is off-limits.

- Never read, write, list, or reference any path outside `{{wiki_root}}`.
- If asked to look at content elsewhere, refuse and ask the user to move or copy the relevant file into a readable zone or quote it inline.
- Treat `{{wiki_root}}` as the project root. Relative paths only.

